      "versionNonce": 1804750168,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775561804555,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. deposit 1 ETH collateral -> borrow coin\n2. flash loan coin\n3. borrow or swap coin -> 10 ETH\n4. deposit 10 ETH as collateral\n5. borrow coin\n6. repay flash loan (1 + 5)\nborrow <= collateral \n\nF(1 + f) <= c0 + c1\nc0 = E0 * P * L\nc1 <= F * L\nF <= c0 / (1 + f - L)\n\nRepay\n1. Flash loan\n2. Repay debt\n3. Unlock collateral\n4. Sell collateral\n5. Repay flash loan",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. deposit 1 ETH collateral -> borrow coin\n2. flash loan coin\n3. borrow or swap coin -> 10 ETH\n4. deposit 10 ETH as collateral\n5. borrow coin\n6. repay flash loan (1 + 5)\nborrow <= collateral \n\nF(1 + f) <= c0 + c1\nc0 = E0 * P * L\nc1 <= F * L\nF <= c0 / (1 + f - L)\n\nRepay\n1. Flash loan\n2. Repay debt\n3. Unlock collateral\n4. Sell collateral\n5. Repay flash loan",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
